        <p style="margin: 0; font-weight: 600; color: #1e3c72;">üåø Conservation Organizations</p>
        <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px; margin: 8px 0 0 0;">NGOs and international conservation organizations that work on marine biodiversity protection and ecosystem management. They bring global expertise and conservation focus to local planning.</p>
      </div>

      <div style="background: #f8f9fa; padding: 18px; border-radius: 6px; border-left: 4px solid #2a5298;">
        <p style="margin: 0; font-weight: 600; color: #1e3c72;">üë• Community Organizations</p>
        <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px; margin: 8px 0 0 0;">Fishing associations, women's groups, and community-based organizations that represent the voices and priorities of coastal residents. They are our foundation.</p>
      </div>

      <div style="background: #f8f9fa; padding: 18px; border-radius: 6px; border-left: 4px solid #2a5298;">
        <p style="margin: 0; font-weight: 600; color: #1e3c72;">üíº Development Partners</p>
        <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px; margin: 8px 0 0 0;">Donor organizations, bilateral and multilateral agencies that provide funding and technical support. Their investment helps scale LMSP successes across Tanzania.</p>
      </div>

      <div style="background: #f8f9fa; padding: 18px; border-radius: 6px; border-left: 4px solid #2a5298;">
        <p style="margin: 0; font-weight: 600; color: #1e3c72;">üè¢ Private Sector</p>
        <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px; margin: 8px 0 0 0;">Tourism operators, aquaculture businesses, and fishing companies. Private sector engagement ensures marine spatial plans account for economic realities.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p>We believe that LMSP is stronger when it brings together these different perspectives. Government agencies bring regulatory authority. Research institutions bring evidence. Conservation organizations bring ecosystem focus. Communities bring lived experience. Development partners bring resources. The private sector brings economic reality. Together, we create solutions that are more robust, more fair, and more likely to endure.</p>

    <div class="cta-section">
      <h3 style="color: #1e3c72; border: none; margin-top: 0;">ü§ù Ready to Partner With Us?</h3>
      <p>We're always interested in new partnerships and collaborations. Whether you represent a community eager to implement LMSP, an organization with resources to contribute, or a government agency ready to mainstream these approaches‚Äîwe want to hear from you.</p>
      <a href="contacts.qmd">Get in Touch Today</a>
    </div>
